cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.DS 

The paper deals with modeling cascade processes in multi-agent systems, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), systems and control (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The use of logic programming and algorithms for finding minimal models further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
